[Missiles Increase After Used ( R1+Triangle=On // R1+X=Off )]
author=12345
description=Can firing left and right missiles

For primary missiles, turn Off before reach 255 missiles, and turn On again before reach 1 missiles.

For secondary missiles, turn Off before reach 255 missiles ( secondary missiles max only 99 missiles ) so turn Off after reach 99 twice and before 55 missiles, and turn On again after reach 99 twice and before 1 missiles
